Description:
AMAZING OPPORTUNITY IN DOCKLANDS
Whether you are a first home buyer or an astute investor, don’t miss out on this incredible chance to buy in the Docklands. Located on La Trobe Street where Docklands meets the CBD sits the Lacrosse Building, ideally located next to Etihad Stadium, public transport, restaurants and shopping.
This 2 bed, 1 bath, 1 car apartment, which has fantastic views of the Etihad Stadium, includes a modern kitchen with stone bench tops and dishwasher, mirrored built in robes in the bedrooms, and clean, contemporary finishes in the bathroom. A Euro-laundry and private balcony round out this well designed apartment.
Completing this apartment is split system heating/cooling, secure swipe/intercom entry, and a secure car space, as well as use of the outdoor pool and gym. Whether you’re enjoying eating out with friends, swimming, shopping, or attending sporting events at Etihad Stadium, this is low maintenance living without the price tag.
Insights: 1315/673 La Trobe Street, Docklands VIC 3008 was last sold in 2017 and 275 other 2 bedroom unit in Docklands have recently been sold.

Description:
URGENT SALE - LUXURIOUS 'CONVESSO' WATERFRONT LIVING - 78 SQM ONE BEDROOM + STUDY
Phone Enquiry ID:34931
The address says it all. This very spacious, luxury Docklands apartment, perched high on the 6th floor of the iconic, 5-star “Convesso Concavo” building, is definitely no exception. Absolute ‘Waterside’ positioning, boasting spectacular water views over the vibrant, Victoria Harbour.
Watch the yachts and other craft wash past in the afternoon sunshine. As evening approaches and the sun sets, the scene before you, completely transforms with thousands of harbour city lights.
Designed by award-winning architects, Bates Smart, and built to a discerning standard, this generous 78 sqm indoor/outdoor space offers excellent proportions and designer finishes throughout, maximising light and flow-through ventilation with floor-to-ceiling windows/doors to capture the amazing views.
- Internal Area of 70 sqm, plus 8 sqm balcony with amazing
water and city views
- One bedroom with two, double mirrored robes
- Dedicated Study nook
- Designer bathroom and European laundry
- Gourmet kitchen with Blanco electric oven, induction cooktop,
concealed dishwasher, stone benchtop, plenty of sleek
cabinetry, modern tile splashback
- Spacious open plan living and dining, opening to balcony
- External storage cage
- Centralised heating and cooling system
- Ample storage: double linen cupboard, bathroom/laundry
storage, kitchen storage, bedroom
- Fibre-optic broadband
- Video Intercom
- Secure building entrance and lift access
Convenience of this outstanding, walk-to-anywhere location:
- A tram stop inside the FREE Tram Zone at your doorstep; 4-
stop no transfer route to Southern Cross Station
- Steps away from Woolworth’s Supermarket, Australia Post
- Next to the ‘Library At The Dock’
- Minutes walk to South Wharf DFO, Harbour Town Shopping
Centre
- Surrounded by promenade and parks, with plenty of cafes,
restaurants and pubs around
- Etihad Stadium
- Direct access to Melbourne CBD via Collins Street
- Corporate offices: NAB, ANZ, Commonwealth Bank, MYER,
KPMG
Exclusive, World-Class Building Facilities:
- 24 hour Concierge
- 25m indoor heated pool, spa and sauna
- Gym and treatment room
- Sky Garden with BBQ facilities
- Cinema Room
- Residents Lounge
- Business lounge
- Conference room
Insights: 6A/8 Waterside Place, Docklands VIC 3008 was last sold in 2017 and 141 other 1 bedroom unit in Docklands have recently been sold.

Description:
Enjoy the Expanses of this Luxury Docklands Retreat
Stunningly high on the 31st floor and exhibiting memorable CBD views, expansive internal living, and luxuriously appointed style that will amaze all buyers, this exceptional 3 bedroom + study, 2 bathroom apartment is sheer Docklands bliss that needs to be seen to be believed.
An astonishing amount of natural light, bright floor-to-ceiling windows, stone benchtops, and premium fittings are just the tip of the iceberg for this dazzling property located in the popular Yarra’s Edge. It’s hard to go past the awe-inspiring vistas found throughout the apartment (to the north, west, and south), with the undercover balcony the ultimate spot to enjoy views of the city as well as the Yarra River and Docklands.
A generous living and dining zone includes the state of the art kitchen with a handy island bench and stainless steel Miele appliances. The master bedroom promises terrific privacy and includes a walk-in robe and gorgeous double vanity ensuite with freestanding bath (plus windows with views), while the other bedrooms with BIRs sit opposite a central bathroom that is truly elegant. There is also a large study which could be used as an office for those who work from home.
Other property additions are a separate laundry room, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, storage cage, two car spaces, and access to an on-site gym as well as RekDek which includes a gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
On top of all these amazing extras, you get to enjoy the fantastic Yarra’s Edge precinct which is one of the most sought-after areas in the Docklands. You’re close to the South Wharf Promenade which has bars and eateries such as Plus 5 Bar, Munich Brauhaus, Citizen Café and Bar, and Common Man, while you’re also near the Melbourne Exhibition Centre, DFO shopping, Crown Casino, Etihad Stadium, Polly Woodside, trams, and Southern Cross Station.
Insights: 62 other 3 bedroom unit in Docklands have recently been sold.

Description:
Designed by Architect, "John Wardle" with Spectacular views of Melbourne's most iconic sights.
Pop open the champagne and watch the explosion of fireworks light up the sky from this 9th floor apartment which is prestigiously located in the "Dock 5 building" and takes in uninterrupted views stretching across the glistening Marina towards New Quay, over to Etihad Stadium and the Melbourne Observation Wheel.
Lavished with space, this secure apartment, designed by renowned Architect, "John Wardle" offers three generous bedrooms with built-in robes and the master bedroom is where you can wake up to the breathtaking vistas and enjoy your morning coffee on the sun-drenched balcony! You will never grow tired of the luxury as it features a modern ensuite adorned with twin basins and a bath while the rest of the bedrooms are serviced by a stylish contemporary bathroom featuring a European laundry.
A generous open-plan living/dining area features swathes of glass so that you can take a front-row seat to enjoy the unspoiled panoramic vistas and can entertain on the balcony overlooking Melbourne's most iconic sights!
Furthermore, a gourmet kitchen with a pantry, Smeg appliances, secure access with an intercom, ducted heating, cooling, a study nook, two car spaces and a storage cage adds the finishing touches to this lifestyle opportunity or lucrative investment which is within walking distance to the CBD, Southbank Promenade restaurants, The Arts Centre, Melbourne Exhibition Centre and Crown Casino. There are also facilities such as a heated indoor pool, gymnasium and recreational outdoor BBQ area.

Description:
Colourful and Lively Docklands Retreat with Water Views
An outstanding blend of contemporary character, lively colour and luxury fittings and fixtures has produced this brand new one bedroom apartment with sort after Victoria Harbour views in the recently completed Gold Tower, which is part of the exclusive Aqui development.
With a superb location in the NewQuay precinct and ideal for investors, first home purchasers and everyone in between, you’ll love the open layout and ultra-modern charm of this 18th floor apartment. Embrace the open living and meals zone with floor to ceiling windows, while a stone kitchen just off this area is fitted with never before used appliances.
An undercover balcony has a southerly aspect and is ideal for alfresco relaxing, while back inside, you also benefit from a comfortable bedroom with BIR and views, stylish bathroom, European laundry, reverse cycle cooling and secure intercom. Also enjoy a 25m indoor pool, spa, sauna, gym, library, private meeting rooms, lush rooftop garden and secure on-site bicycle storage as part of the building.
This amazing location means you’re just steps to the fabulous Harbour Town Shopping Centre. Set to undergo a $150m revamp, this amazing retail hub has a great assortment of fashion outlets as well as eateries including Le Cirque, Coffee Club, Nando’s and Sun Churro. You also have access to promenade restaurants, IGA X-Press, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, and the 30, 75 and 86 trams going all over Melbourne.
Investors take note, with a conservative rental appraisal of $410 per week, this property will gross 5.4% if purchased for $396,000.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
Style and Light on the Cusp of the City
With a terrific place on the 6th floor of the Lacrosse residential complex which is positioned right next to Etihad Stadium, this excellent two bedroom, two bathroom apartment promises stylish and relaxed living ideal for every type of buyer.
Impressive light and open living can be enjoyed in the sizeable lounge and dining space, which opens out to a north-facing balcony with fantastic views. The kitchen comes with stone countertops and stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher, and is an airy space to prepare breakfast, lunch, and dinner with no drama.
Both comfortable bedrooms have built-in robes including the master haven that comes with its own ensuite. Further enjoy a quality main bathroom, European laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom entry, and access to a pool with deck and gym.
The Lacrosse complex is in the Stadium Precinct but also has easy access to Digital Harbour and the NewQuay Precinct. Take advantage of ground floor eateries including MOMAMI restaurant and Khaza Ghar Café, while you have La Trobe Street trams pretty much at your doorstep. You’re also a short walk to Flagstaff Gardens, city shopping, and Southern Cross Station.
Please contact Vicky Leong on 0452 486 860 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
Yarra’s Edge Excellence with Exceptional Floorplan
One of the absolute modern delights of the Yarra’s Edge precinct thanks to its multiple living zones which offer brilliant light, sophisticated style, and unbelievable views, this 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom corner apartment is an outright superstar.
This amazing property boasts a plethora of floor-to-ceiling windows which permits for spectacular views of the city skyline as well as the Yarra River. The expansive central living zone gets inviting natural light while offering ample spaces to lounge and dine. Adjoining this main zone is the tiled stone kitchen with Miele appliances and a cosy space for casual meals.
The master bedroom delivers a double basin ensuite and BIR's, while other bedrooms with excellent storage have easy access to the main bathroom as well as an additional powder room. The large balcony is a wonderful area for outdoor entertaining, with extras including a laundry, ducted heating and cooling, storage cage, 2 car spaces, secure intercom, and access to RekDek which includes a gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
The Yarra’s Edge is a coveted destination for those looking to make the Docklands change, where you’ll be located close to the amazing South Wharf Promenade which has terrific bars and restaurants as well as easy access to DFO shopping. You’re also close to Crown Entertainment Complex, Southbank Promenade, and the Victoria Harbour precinct just over the bridge.

Description:
Stunning Bay Views from the 36th Floor
Positioned right on the banks of the iconic Yarra River and showcasing stylishly modern and generous apartment living, this two bedroom residence with the added bonus of two secure car spaces is destined to have extensive appeal.
Enjoying a unique floorplan and a wonderful presentation, this abode on the 36th floor has all your bases covered. Full height windows allow for fabulous views from the spacious living and meals zone, with this central hub stepping outside onto the balcony where you can further experience superb vistas of the tranquil Port Phillip Bay.
The tiled kitchen promises a moveable island bench fitted with stone as well as stainless steel Miele appliances. Both bedrooms boast an amazing amount of space and are equipped with built-in robes (one of the bedrooms has balcony access), meanwhile the well-appointed bathroom features dual vanities and a spa bath. Other property extras include a separate laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, and access to RekDek which includes a gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
It is hard to go past the Yarra’s Edge precinct as a living destination thanks to its close proximity to DFO Shopping and South Wharf Promenade which enjoys an abundance of bars and eateries including The General Assembly, Meat Market, The Boatbuilders Yard, Charlie Lovett, and Munich Brauhaus. You’re also near Crown Casino, CBD, and public transport including Southern Cross Station.

Description:
Stylish NewQuay Precinct Living with City Vistas
Experience a genuinely stylish and low-maintenance Docklands lifestyle with this single bedroom apartment, which offers gorgeous CBD views and a place in the sleek Quays residential complex.
This 8th floor apartment is superbly easy to care for and represents a great opportunity for first home buyers, city workers and investors with appealing rental returns. Sensational city views can be enjoyed from the sizeable living and meals zone, bright bedroom with built-in robes and the undercover balcony which is ideal for weekend drinks and summer meals
The kitchen boasts a stone benchtop and stainless steel appliances, the flawless bathroom is wonderfully styled, while other highlights include a European laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom and a secure car space. Access a Health Club featuring a swimming pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium and a yoga studio, as well as the Resident’s Club on Level One with a library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room & cinema lounge. There is also a rooftop garden with BBQ and dining facilities.
The NewQuay precinct is a thriving hub and the base for some of the Docklands best attractions. Surrounding restaurants cover cuisines of all types including The Conder restaurant, New Quay International Buffet, Achelya Restaurant, Woolshed, Berth & Cargo. You’re also moments to Harbour Town Shopping Centre (soon to undergo a $150m makeover to bring in new stores such as H&M, Hoyts Cinema, Strike Bowling & Woolworths), Costco, Etihad Stadium, Festival Hall and easy tram access.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304

OPULENT DOCKLANDS TOWNHOUSE
You will be awestruck upon entering this grand townhouse in Docklands. Consisting of approximately 320sqm of internal living space, this townhouse oozes opulence with its 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, 2 car park garage, and rooftop deck taking in views of Victoria Harbour and the Bolte Bridge.
Ground floor features:
- Large bedroom/media room with BIRs
- Bathroom

- Wine cellar
- 2 car garage
1st Floor Features

2nd Floor Features

Rounding out this superb residence is an elevator, ducted heating and cooling throughout, security system and intercom entry. Located only minutes from City Link and the CBD, and metres from the waterfront, this amazing townhouse is executive living at its finest.

Description:
SENSATIONAL LOCATION, ARCHITECTURE, AND DESIGN
An amazing opportunity awaits for investors or owner occupiers alike in this as new, corner apartment in the chic M Docklands Complex. On offer is this beautifully contemporary apartment with remarkable styling, and the option of all furniture and appliances included. Situated on La Trobe Street where Docklands meets the CBD, you’ll be amazed by the stunning finishes in this sensational location.
The open plan kitchen/dining area includes a stone bench-top island with breakfast bar, concealed dishwasher, Bosch oven and cooktop, concealed fridge, and plenty of clever storage solutions. The light-filled living room flows out onto the balcony with views to the east and north. Both bedrooms come with mirrored BIRs, the master including a study nook and ensuite. Both bathrooms are strikingly designed with light timber finishes, black fixtures, and subway tiling in the shower, which features a rain-shower head.
Rounding out this remarkable apartment is a Euro-laundry, secure swipe and video intercom entry, secure ground level car space, and storage cage. Typical of modern apartment living residents enjoy the use of the complex's gym and heated outdoor swimming pool. With all appliances included and the apartment barely lived-in, this is the very definition of a turn-key property.
With public transport, world class shopping, and an array of waterside restaurants and bars on your doorstep, this well laid out pad is perfectly situated only minutes from the CBD and CityLink.

Ample windows flood each room with natural light, and offer sensational views spanning over the harbour and marina.
The Concavo building has set the highest of standards for a waterfront lifestyle with resort style facilities to enjoy on a daily basis. The amenities of this luxurious building include:
- 24 hour concierge
- Residents Lounge
- Business Centre & Board Room
- Indoor Cinema
- North facing Sky Garden facing the water, with BBQ facilities
- 25 metre indoor heated pool, spa and sauna
- Gymnasium and treatment room
-Two secured car spaces on the same level as the apartment and one secured storage cage.
- Free trams at your doorstep with award winning restaurants and the new public library and children’s park nearby.
This is the complete package for easy living in a sensational location.
Call Lyle now to arrange a private inspection.

Description:
Love the Parkside Lifestyle and Amazing CBD and River Views
Making a genuine statement with memorable views of the marina and CBD, luxury modern style, and a place in the desired Yarra’s Edge precinct which is bursting with stunning food, drink, and shopping options, this sophisticated two bedroom, two bathroom apartment will impress all!
This exceptional property is superbly placed on the 17th floor of the Yarra Point complex, which has access to fantastic RekDek facilities which includes a gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna. This area is also near fabulous South Wharf restaurants and bars including Common Man and Plus 5 Bar, while other attractions including Direct Factory Outlet, Crown Casino, Melbourne Exhibition Centre, Docklands Park, Spencer Street trams, and Southern Cross Station are all nearby.
Enjoying bright floor-to-ceiling windows, stone benchtops, quality fittings and fixtures, and a thoughtful layout, this inspired dwelling will have widespread appeal. The generous lounge and dining space flows out to a charmed undercover balcony which is the ideal spot to soak in the brilliant city and Yarra River vistas, meanwhile back inside and the kitchen has everything you need including a gleaming glass splashback, stone island bench, and stainless steel Miele appliances.
Both bedrooms come complete with built-in robes including the master bedroom which features a pristine double vanity ensuite, while other features include a central bathroom, European laundry, ducted heat/cool, video intercom, and one secure car space. You also have direct park frontage to complete this amazing package!
